1. Improve graphic presentation of Hacon graph
2. Change the name of the rules, these are the names used
   by Ohmoto:
   - N1, N2, N3, N4 -> K (kasanie: tangency)
                 K0 = N4, K1 = N3,N2, K2 = N1
   - N5             -> T (triple-point)
                 T0 se il triangolino dentro ha f = 0
		 T1 se il triangolino dentro ha f = 2
   - C1             -> L (lip)
   - C2             -> B (beak-to-beak)
   - CN1            -> S (swallowtail)
   - CN3            -> C (cusp crossing)
                 C0 se la cuspide sta tutta a sx dell'arco
		 C1 altrimenti
